Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the whole world only had left hands{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.02,STAFF - 方正小标宋_GBK-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\fade(300,500)\blur0.3\bord0\b0\fscy104\3a80\pos(1130,292)}时间轴
